keyword: * -a -t titleFixed='Supershell - Inject' -t disableLeaveAlert=true -t disableReconnect=true ssh -J rssh:*
metadata_description: Supershell is a C2 remote control platform accessed through WEB services. By establishing a reverse SSH tunnel it obtains a fully interactive Shell and supports multi-platform architecture Payload
